<bibRefCitation author="Post A. &amp; Quero J. - C." box="[460,695,1390,1416]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" pagination="111 - 128" refId="ref43104" refString="Post A. &amp; Quero J. - C. 1991. Distribution et taxonomie des Howella (Perciformes, Percichthyidae) de l'Atlantique. Cybium 15 (2): 111 - 128." type="journal article" year="1991">Post &amp; Quéro, 1991</bibRefCitation>
